eferrer\" class=\"underline\">Loro&#x27;s Rich Text CRDT</a>, to learn more.</p></main></article><article class=\"Card_Container__V_RLV relative md:w-4/5 lg:w-3/4 even:self-start odd:self-end md:p-7.5 md:after:content-[&#x27;&#x27;] md:before:content-[&#x27;&#x27;]\"><main class=\"Card_Card__7QGnj\"><div class=\"relative w-10 h-10 md:w-15 md:h-15\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 40 40\" class=\"absolute inset-0\"><path fill=\"url(#icon-line_svg__a)\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M21.284 12.074c-.397.157-.83.243-1.284.243-.484 0-.945-.098-1.364-.276l-3.498 5.186a3.492 3.492 0 1 1-1.27-.614l3.618-5.364a3.492 3.492 0 1 1 4.968.061l3.592 5.325A3.496 3.496 0 0 1 30.476 20a3.492 3.492 0 1 1-5.68-2.721l-3.512-5.205Z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path><path fill=\"url(#icon-line_svg__b)\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M14.3 23.248c-.397.158-.83.244-1.284.244a3.48 3.48 0 0 1-1.364-.276l-3.497 5.186a3.492 3.492 0 1 1-1.27-.614l3.617-5.364a3.492 3.492 0 1 1 4.968.061l3.592 5.325a3.497 3.497 0 0 1 4.43 3.365 3.492 3.492 0 1 1-5.68-2.721L14.3 23.248Z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path><path fill=\"url(#icon-line_svg__c)\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M28.269 23.248c-.398.158-.831.244-1.285.244a3.48 3.48 0 0 1-1.363-.276l-3.498 5.186a3.492 3.492 0 1 1-1.27-.614l3.617-5.364a3.492 3.492 0 1 1 4.968.06l3.592 5.326a3.496 3.496 0 0 1 4.43 3.365 3.492 3.492 0 1 1-5.68-2.721l-3.511-5.206Z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path><defs><linearGradient id=\"icon-line_svg__a\" x1=\"9.524\" x2=\"30.326\" y1=\"5.333\" y2=\"6.833\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><stop stop-color=\"#98B0FF\"></stop><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"#42FFA4\"></stop></linearGradient><linearGradient id=\"icon-line_svg__b\" x1=\"2.54\" x2=\"23.343\" y1=\"16.508\" y2=\"18.008\" gradientUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><stop stop-color=\"#98B0FF\"></stop><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"#42FFA4\"></stop></linearGradient><linearGradient id=\"icon-line_svg__c\" x1=\"16.508\" x2=\"37.311\" y1=\"16.508\" y2=\"18.008\